  "slug": "gala-pie",
  "title": "Gala Pie",
  "subtitle": "A large raised pork pie with a row of hard-boiled eggs embedded in the filling",
  "excerpt": "Gala pie is a pork pie with one distinguishing feature: three or four hard-boiled eggs buried lengthways in the filling before baking. When sliced, every piece reveals a circle of egg in the centre of the pork filling. It is the British butcher's classic cold centrepiece.",
  "type": "RECIPE",
  "sourceNotes": "Traditional British butcher's raised pie. Book of Household Management (1861, Project Gutenberg #10136): raised pie methods. British pork pie tradition, Yorkshire and East Midlands variants.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Gala pie is a pork pie with hard-boiled eggs running down the centre of the filling. Sliced cold, every piece shows a circle of egg set in the pork. It follows the same method as a standard pork pie, with one extra step: packing the filling firmly around the eggs so there are no air pockets. The pie is built in a large loaf tin and unmoulded after baking and chilling."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Use a "
          },
          {
            "text": "hand-raised pastry",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termId": "cmpdr473d0000hov4etoqgkey"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " technique or, more practically at home, line a well-greased loaf tin. The "
          },
          {
            "text": "aspic jelly",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termId": "cmpdr47410001hov41yo2hicg"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " is poured in after baking through the steam hole in the lid."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "What you need"
          }
        ]
      },
